# Homebrew formula template for ccync — cross-agent plugin / MCP / skills manager
# Placeholders (fill in from checksums.txt after publishing the GitHub Release):
#   {{VERSION}}             — exact GitHub Release tag (e.g. v0.1.0); used in URLs
